overview:
Maps International is a global provider of wall maps and other mapping products, we have one of the largest ranges of maps worldwide. www.maps-international.com serves the US market and currently ships only to the US. All our products are made and shipped from our manufacturing and distribution centre in Wisconsin, US.

The Maps International online map shop was launched in 2003 selling just a few of our most popular World Wall Maps. The range of products has grown to a varied map collection of wall maps, which still includes our famous world wall maps, continental wall maps, art maps plus a huge amount more.

In addition to our range of wall maps, we offer a custom map service allowing a map to be made to fit any requirement. We utilise our parent companies hugely experienced cartographic and GIS team to provide this service. With over 40 years in the mapping industry Lovell Johns is our parent company. Lovell Johns provide map making and geographic solutions to many Government Agencies, publishers and all sizes of business.

Maps International also has websites for the UK - www.mapsinternational.co.uk and Germany - www.de.maps-international.com.
